{"tid":112463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【三星再出事】產S8電池天津廠起火冒濃煙 網民：有爆炸","createTime":"2017-02-08T07:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T10:05:09.000Z","uid":38173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b049cc936af552eeabe968027a1ad402b2700fee","tid":112463,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>【三星再出事】產S8電池天津廠起火冒濃煙 網民：有爆炸</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170208/large/1486534603_b479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F1486534603_b479.jpg&h=65b5eb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170208/large/1486534601_e4ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F1486534601_e4ac.jpg&h=e97c9c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三星電池生產商天津SDI工廠今早起火，廠房冒出黑煙。有網民在微博爆料，聽聞是工廠爆炸。另據悉，事發時有約600名員工在工廠內。目前大火已受控，有關方面正清理火場，當局未有透露是否有人傷亡，起火原因待查。不過，內媒就重提，去年三星Note7手機爆炸，三星官方就指SDI電池供應商的設計存在問題。<br />\n工資資料顯示，三星SDI是三星集團在電子領域的附屬企業，屬中國三星的顯像管生產部門。另據官網資料顯示，三星SDI在長春、合肥、香港、上海、北京、天津、無錫、西安、台灣台北都設有分支機構，其中天津工廠負責電池生產。據悉，該廠正生產三星新一代旗艦機S8的手機電池。<br />\n上海澎湃新聞網引述網上多篇公開報道稱，三星Note7機型去年發生多宗爆炸事故。今年1月中旬，三星官方回應是SDI電池供應商的設計存在問題。另據新浪科技報道，據野村證券分析師估計，2016年三星因電池起火問題召回的Galaxy Note7手機中，有65%的電池由三星SDI供應。<br />\n據彭博報道，三星SDI證實天津工廠出現狀況，稱正在調查。<br />\n隨後央視報道指，三星天津武清區工廠於今晨8時許發生火災，據了解是因該廠堆放的廢舊電池起火。火災發生後，現場約600名員工迅速撤離，未造成人員傷亡。此外，消防部門因考慮到電池為廢舊電池，人為撲滅可能會造成更多危險，故決定採取電池燃燒盡的方法。最終火勢於中午12時30分左右被撲滅。事故原因還在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170208/56276780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170208%2F56276780&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b035522d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170208%2F56276780&h=542539cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170208/56276780</a>"},{"pid":"b049558d3c386f4aeb674223502bb52b020b3f2c","tid":112463,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"今天炸埋自己間廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f586e41cda209b267f38fa862d7f3d90da348869","tid":112463,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BOOM</span></span>"},{"pid":"8dc5016d5d08dc1ede2f0fab48c3397f131d542e","tid":112463,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"天津第二爆"},{"pid":"4009b83a84711a28bb4b14f2c7ab1eee776cdf3e","tid":112463,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天津第二爆</blockquote><br />\n蘑菇節紀念日"},{"pid":"031df307f6e41024770c4e091686460298358e81","tid":112463,"uid":13389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次過燒毀<br />\n順手燒埋哩度個啲shamesung 打手<br />\n一個個放埋入去<br />\n個啲乜老貓呀<br />\nOn9 peter 仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19ce3f46e3f49da45698bf0bc271f8569baade9","tid":112463,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09J1tD8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F